<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361622>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14 Habitus of Rotundicephala gen. n. spp. A, R. pacifica comb. n.; B, ditto, female; C, R. koreana comb. n.; D, R. koheii sp. n., male (holotype). Scale bar: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361622/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361624>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15 Genitalia and antenna of Rotundicephala gen n. A, B & G, R. pacifica comb. n. (A, median lobe of aedeagus; B, spermatheca; G, right antenna); C, D & H, R. koreana comb. n. (C, median lobe of aedeagus; D, spermatheca; H, right antenna); E, F & I, R. koheii sp. n. (E, median lobe of aedeagus; F, spermatheca; I, right antenna). Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361624/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361673>
    dc:description "FIGURE 25 Distribution and habitat of Rotundicephala gen. n. spp. of Japan. A, known localities in Japan (red circle, R. pacifica comb. n. (red ring, type locality)); blue square, R. koheii sp. n.; yellow triangle, R. koreana comb. n.); B, habitat of R. koheii sp. n. (Kanagawa-ken, Japan); C, habitat of R. pacifica comb. n. (Tsushima, adults of Diaulota submarina was collected same time)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361673/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

